Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:09.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,今年　７９歳になる　緒原ショウスケさんの朝は早い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:14.20,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ショウスケさんの朝の日課はまず　ラジオ体操をして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そして散歩に出かける
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:22.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ゆっくり時間をかけて　住宅街を歩いたあとは　公園でひと休みだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:28.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,たまにリュウマチが痛むが　いたって元気である
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,はぁ　いい朝じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:36.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,集中しろ　翔真
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:37.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,目をそらすんじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:40.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,でもあのじいさん本当に…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:40.44,TXT JP (UP) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,もうすぐだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:43.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そんな緒原ショウスケさんの楽しみは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:48.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そおーれ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:49.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,今だ　行けっ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:54.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そおーれ　豆をおあがり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,今日の豆は一段と香ばしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:00.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,おいしいですね　りんね様
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:06.54,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,黄泉の羽織を着た六道りんねと死神翔真は　普通の人には見えないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,これが朝飯かーい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:48.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,このじいさんをお迎えに来たんじゃねぇのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,失礼な事を言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:57.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ショウスケさんは　まだまだお元気だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:00.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あれっ　翔真くんじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,成仏実習　まだ終わってないの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:09.05,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,死神小学校のクラスメートか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ボクたち実習終わって　これからあの世に帰るところなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:16.64,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,へー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,５０ポイント　やっと集まったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:23.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ここで　成仏ポイントについて説明しておこう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:26.99,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,虫や金魚を成仏させると１点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,小鳥は２点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.82,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,犬や猫だと５点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そして　普通に寿命を迎えた人間は１０点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:42.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,これらを５０点集めれば　成仏実習は合格となる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ボクは猫と小鳥で集めたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ボクは犬と虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,翔真くんは今何ポイント
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:59.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,おれは小動物でちまちまポイント稼ぐのは性に合わないんでな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.17,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪霊狙ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:07.34,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,人間の悪霊の場合　ボーナスポイントが５０点で　一発合格なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:10.34,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,へー　さっすが翔真くん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ボクら　悪霊なんてこわくて近づけないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.35,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,おれもすぐあの世に戻るぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,がんばってね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,お〜っ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,見栄っ張りですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,いつあの世に戻れるやら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,うるせぇ　貧乏人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,うまい　うまいな　この豆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ですね　りんね様
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,くっそ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,どっかに悪霊いねぇかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.23,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪霊　紹介してやろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,誰だよ　おまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:51.71,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,見てたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:56.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,よりによって貧乏なりんねくんの所にホームステイさせられるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:58.20,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,かわいそうな子だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,りんねを知ってるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まあね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,それよりついておいで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:12.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,翔真くんのそばにいるの…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:15.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,羽を隠しているけど　悪魔の魔狭人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,魔狭人とは　色々あって六道りんねを怨んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,心の狭い悪魔である
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:26.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,どきな　ガキども　邪魔なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.97,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ったく　歩きにくいったらありゃしない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:34.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,最近の若いモンは　お年寄りに道を譲るって事を知らないのかねぇ　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まったく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,どうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:42.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,やった　あの意地悪そうな顔　間違いなく悪霊だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:45.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,所詮は子供
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:49.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ただ顔のコワい意地悪ばあさんと悪霊の見分けもつかないとは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:55.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,だが子供の死神といえども　罪のない霊を傷つける事は許されない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:03.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,その子供死神の罪は　ホームステイ先のりんねくんの監督責任となる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,なんてすばらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.47,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,困るだろうなあ　りんねくん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪霊　覚悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.65,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ダメだよ翔真くん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.32,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そのおばあさんは普通の…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:23.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,これだから最近の子は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.17,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,生きてるのがイヤになるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:31.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まったく　年長者を敬うって事知らないのかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ちょっと　聞いてんのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:37.47,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,この人は普通の霊だから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.73,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪霊そのものじゃねぇかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あんたね　魔狭人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,翔真くんをそそのかしたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,とんだ言いがかりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,僕はその子を救おうとしただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:54.49,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,六道くん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:56.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,デビルスモーク
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,辛くなったら　いつでもおいで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:07.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,翔真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,やつとは二度と会うな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,魔狭人は悪魔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:16.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,やつの狙いは　おれと関わりのあるおまえを失敗させる事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:18.49,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:22.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,さて　おれはこの御婦人をお送りしてくるが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,へー　最近の若いモンにしちゃ珍しく親切だねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,見学を兼ねて　一緒に来るか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:30.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,やだね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,のんびり見学してる暇なんてねぇし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,翔真くん…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:42.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,なんだこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:46.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,手紙と…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ご　五百円
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:52.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,これで奴きな物を書いなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.23,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,僕は君の見方だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:59.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,一部誤字はあるが　原文どおりである
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.34,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,魔狭人おにいさん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:07.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,貧乏りんねなんぞより　ずっといい人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:10.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,わかってくれたかい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ついでにこれもプレゼントだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:18.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,きみの死神のカマに装備したまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:21.20,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,これは？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.72,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪霊センサーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,きみを悪霊の所へ導いてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,おまけにカマの威力もパワーアップだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ほ　本当か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,よーし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:35.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,これで貧乏生活ともおさらばだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:36.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,魔狭人おにいさん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:51.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,いや　１時間目から体育とは　爽やかで気持ちいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,どこが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:53.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,だるい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そういえば　桜ちゃんどうしたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,また急用かな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:00.75,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:04.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,なまぬるい風が気持ちいい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,さ　張り切っていくぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,すっげ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:20.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,なんか急に悪霊が集まってきたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪霊センサーなんぞ真っ赤なウソ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:34.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あれは周りの霊を集め　ことごとく悪霊化させる　いわば悪霊製造装置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:36.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あの装置の力で
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:40.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,翔真は不正に作られた悪霊を狩りまくる事になる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:44.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,さて　罪もない悪霊を狩ったその監督責任　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:49.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,りんねくんはどう取るつもりかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,その頃　六道りんねは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,本当に情けないねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:10:00.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まるでこっちの声が聞こえないみたいにわざと無視してさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,本当そうですよねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:04.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,このあいだもヒドイんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:11.30,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,バスに乗ろうとしたら　運転手がいきなり走り出しちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まるであたしが見えてないみたいにさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まあ　それは災難でしたねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,その…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうそう　こんな事もあったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:25.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,信号が青なんで　横断歩道を渡ろうとしたらさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,お話が弾んでいるところ申し訳ないんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:30.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そろそろ輪廻の輪に…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:31.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,なに言ってんだい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,この人が通りかかってくれなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:37.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あんたあたしを追い出すつもりだったんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.09,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あの鬼嫁みたいにさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.39,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,誰だ　鬼嫁って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと聞いてあげなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,霊のグチを聞くのも死神の仕事よ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,年寄り同士だと話が合うんだろうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:53.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,と　し　よ　り？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:53.90,TXT JP (UP) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,いでででで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:59.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,今どきの若いモンにはいい薬だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:02.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,で　どこまで話したっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:03.81,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,銀行に行ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:07.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,窓口のおねえさんに呼んでもらえなかったところまでですね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:11.32,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あっ　そうそう　それがヒドイ話でさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:14.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ずっと座ってるのに　無視されっぱなしで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まあ　ヒドイ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪霊　覚悟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:33.32,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,すっげえ　カマの斬れ味が今までと全然違う
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:37.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,今日はこんなにたくさんパンの耳が手に入った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,りんね様も喜ぶぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,こうなったら　斬って斬って斬りまくってやるぜっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,こらっ　翔真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,邪魔すんじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,パンの耳が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,街中悪霊だらけ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あ　六文ちゃん　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:11.97,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,どうなってるの　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.09,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あれです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,翔真くん　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:18.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,カマに何かが…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あれは悪魔の道具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:25.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,近づいた霊を悪霊化させる悪霊製造装置なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:28.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪魔の道具　という事は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,魔狭人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,大漁だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:43.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,この悪霊達は全員僕が地獄に連れて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,すげえ　すげえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,これが俺の本当の力なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あれじゃ　翔真くんまるで…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪魔の手先ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:00.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,疲れた　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:02.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ったく　あのばあさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:06.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,私が相手になってあげなきゃ　ずっと説教してたわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:10.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,逆に話を長引かせてたんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.73,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ところで　りんねの所の小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まだ成仏実習終わってないんですって？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.02,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ごまかした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:21.09,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まもなくホームステイ期間は終了よ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.72,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,虫の魂ひとつ集めてない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:27.56,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そう　でも気をつけなさいね　りんね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:31.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そういう児童は　あせって不正に走りやすいから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,この時期よく悪魔に狙われるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,よくわかってるよ　おばあちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:40.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,お　ば　あ　ち　ゃ　んって言っちゃイヤ～ン
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:41.58,TXT JP (UP) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,いだだだだだだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:48.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,それと以前は児童が不祥事を起こしても
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:52.11,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ホームステイ先のファミリーは始末書だけで済んだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.82,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,今期からすっごい罰金を取られる事になったから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:04.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,桜さまは翔真に話しかけて気をそらしてください
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:05.50,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,それは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.47,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,高い所の悪霊製造装置もラクラク切り離せる　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪魔道具切りバサミです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.73,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あら　便利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ほらほら　どうした　どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,やめなさい　翔真くん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あなた悪魔にダマされているのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:24.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,その悪霊たち本当は罪のない…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:27.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,うっせーな　魔狭人おにいさんはケチくさいりんねなんかより
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:30.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ずっとおれの事考えてくれてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,第一　悪霊１体で実習は終了なんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.50,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,５０００　いや　１万ポイントためて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:39.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,クラスのやつらに自慢してやるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:41.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,スキだらけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:48.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,六文　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,六文ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:53.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪霊センサーを切り離すつもりだったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:57.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,桜っ　邪魔すんじゃねー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.59,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,やめなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:01.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,しまった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,魔狭人おにいさん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:12.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪霊もたっぷり集まったようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.72,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,魔狭人おにいさんのおかげだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.40,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,じゃ　そろそろ行くか　地獄へ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:21.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,だって　おまえは罪のない霊を狩りまくったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:26.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,罪のない　で　でも　悪霊センサーに…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まだ　わからないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:32.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,これは近づく霊を悪霊化させる悪霊製造装置だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:38.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,もう手遅れさ　なにもかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:40.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,よくもだましたな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:45.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,デビルサンダー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,電撃　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,子供相手に本気出してますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:54.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,助けなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:59.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪魔道具切りバサミはビル６階分までのびてとっても便利なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,こら　よせ　危ねっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:06.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,忘れたか　僕は女子供等　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:10.02,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,自分より弱い者にはいっさい手加減しない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,デビルサンダーボール
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:20.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か　真宮桜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:21.30,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,六道くん　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:21.30,TXT JP (UP) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,りんね様
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,りんねくん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,その子を返してもらおうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:37.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,り　りんね　くそっ　体が動かない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:39.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,遅いよ　りんねくん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:43.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,きみの監督責任は徹底的に追求されるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.64,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,君の負けだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:53.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,なんか　すンごい罰金取られるらしいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:57.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,なんか六道くん　すごく怒ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:17:00.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,きっと　正義の怒りですよ　間違いありません
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:04.56,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,スゴんだって無駄だよ　りんねくん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,少しでも妙な動きをしたら　翔真の命は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,いでっ　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:14.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,いた　ちょっ　った　やめっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:20.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,わかった　りんねくんがそこまで言うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,なにも言ってないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ないですね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:25.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,翔真だけは返そう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,見たか　デビルボンバーの威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.17,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,爆弾　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,りんね様
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,さらばだ　りんねくん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:41.54,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,このガキは悪霊達とともに地獄行きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,助けてくれ　　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,これは霊達の声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:54.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,地獄はいやだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:57.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,誰か　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:57.55,TXT JP (UP) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,怖いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.72,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,おれが悪魔の口車に乗ったせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.89,TXT JP (UP) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,いやー
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,罪のない霊達が…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,助けなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:06.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,なにかないか　なにか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:09.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,五百円
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:15.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,これで好きな物を買いなさい　僕は君の見方だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:18.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,繰り返すが　原文どおりである
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,なんでもいい　悪魔を倒す道具を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:31.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.40,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,逃げたかったら逃がしてやってもいいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:44.59,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,さあ　霊達を見捨ててひとり逃げるがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:48.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そうすればもう二度と君を追いかけたりしないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪魔のささやきである
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,助けて　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,こらえてつかぁさい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,神経痛が
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,い　いやだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:00.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,しつこいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:03.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,絶対に放すもんか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あ　あれは授業で習った事がある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:14.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,持ち主を犯罪者の元に導き捕縛する伝説の死神道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:15.31,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,裁きの輪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:17.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,翔真　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:19.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,無事だな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:23.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,りんね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,よかった　間に合って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:28.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,浄化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:39.88,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,終わったか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:41.87,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:48.35,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,悪魔に気を許すとこうなる　勉強になっただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,甘いな　りんねくん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:56.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,預かった児童が不祥事を起こしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:20:00.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,監督不行き届で多額の罰金を取られるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:06.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,今回の翔真が罪なき霊を不正に悪霊化し狩りまくった一件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,僕が当局に告発すれば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,え　今なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,誰にも言いません
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:16.51,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,もみ消した　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:17.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,もみ消した
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,もみ消した
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.50,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,今日のところはこれくらいにしといてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:26.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,覚えていろ　りんねくん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:30.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,こうして　悪魔魔狭人の野望は打ち砕かれた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:33.02,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,しかし　いつ　また地獄の底から
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:37.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,りんねを陥れるためのこそくなわなを仕組んでくるか分からないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:41.82,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,頑張れ　六道りんね　負けるな　六道りんね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:46.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,パンの耳は牛乳に浸して食べてもおいしいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:53.31,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,さて　おれはこの皆様をあの世にお送りするが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.73,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,いかんせん人数が多すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:21:01.17,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,そこで翔真　五名様ほどおまえが成仏のお手伝いをしなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.02,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,い　いいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:09.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,六道くん　確か普通の霊の成仏ポイントが１０点だから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:14.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,五人分で５０点　翔真の成仏実習は終了ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:17.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,だけどいいの　六道くんから譲ってもらって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:21.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,人の助けを借りたらポイント貰えないんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:26.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ああ　しかし　おれは成仏に手を貸さないからセーフだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:29.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,それに　魔狭人にダマされて色々やらかしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:33.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,最後は体を張って　霊達を守ろうとしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:39.47,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,わかっててくれたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:41.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,いいか　翔真
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,霊の皆様の声に耳をかたむけて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,心をこめてお送りするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:49.79,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,それができたら実習は終了だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,それじゃ　行こーか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:56.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,待て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:00.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,おまえのせいでわしら悪霊になっちまったんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさいは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:03.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,え　いや　その
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:05.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさいは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:10.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,あら　大変
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:15.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと正座なさい　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:18.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まったく　最近の若いモンは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:19.71,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:24.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,まぁ　霊のグチの相手をするのも死神の仕事だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:28.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,それから３日間　翔真くんは帰れませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.69,0:24:02.88,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,呪いのワラ人形の話って知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:04.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,ううん　どんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:06.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M-O,,0,0,0,,夜一人で道を歩いていると
